@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.75) - 0.91))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v2 + 0.17) - (tmp + 0.29 * v0 + 0.48)))
    v0 = 0.13
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
